{"tid":2365411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒踢爆 Facebook 澄清 WhatsApp 更新條款係謊言","createTime":"2021-01-13T17:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T03:56:36.000Z","uid":147376,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"781746595f767530eb4a0e4eb6ad90da2facb88b","tid":2365411,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/217553/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F217553%2F1%2F&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=1a2bc713\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/217553/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n近排講得最熱鬧的當然係 WhatsApp 將會係 2 月 8 日強制同意佢最新的用戶條款。 我之前都分享過，唔同意就無辦法繼續用服務了，好多人呼籲大家改用 Signal。Facebook 出來解畫，又話乜有加密唔會偷睇你信息內容，又話唔會將你資料交比第三方。 咁事實上係點？&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp 自己發放左一張自我解釋的圖片，圖片裡面描述 5 個 NO、兩個 YES。而 Facebook 香港負責人都出來澄清，大家可以 Click 入 now 新聞睇番<br />\nFacebook大中華區總裁：WhatsApp對話仍受加密保障<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419929&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419929%26refer%3DShare&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=6d366011\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419929%26refer%3DShare&h=970b2594\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419929&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/993Yqnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F993Yqnj.jpg&h=7c97e75d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有外國媒體相當細心，已經踢爆其中一項：「WhatsApp cannot see your shared location and neither can Facebook」，意思係話不論 Whatsapp 或者 Facebook 都無法睇到你分享的定位。呢個項目就捉晒蟲，比外國媒體正中紅心。因為喺 Whatsapp 的私隱條款中列明，「Automatically Collected Information 」自動收集資料部分清楚列明：當用戶同其他人共享自己目前的定位位置資訊時候，WhatsApp 係會等於獲得你許可收集你手機裝置精準的定位資料，姐係佢知道你身處何方。而更厲害係，哪怕你無用呢個定位功能，Whatsapp 都講明會使用 IP 地址以及其他輔助資料，例如你手機區號 852 咁，大約判斷你身處的範圍。簡單講，不論你用唔用定位功能，Whatsapp 都會知道你位置，只係精確度如何。<br />\n<br />\n根據英文原文描述，如果你唔用定位確實睇唔到你精確位置，而係佢會好努力咁透過不斷收集 IP 去估計你大約位置，例如你經常連接不同的 WiFi，其他人有打開定位，又用同一個 WiFi，咁咪都知道你係邊度囉。外國媒體最後仲補多一刀，話 WhatsApp 解釋話唔會洩露用戶私隱，其實都係講大話，充滿誤導和錯誤的陳述。 因為英文最新條款中「 WhatsApp &nbsp; We work with third-party service providers and other Facebook Companies to help us operate, provide, improve, understand, customise, support, and market our Services」簡單講就係全方位同第三方，包括 Facebook 公司分享你資料。<br />\n<br />\n所以點解今次改條款全世界都咁大反應，因為 WhatsApp 同 Facebook 一樣講一套做一套。"},{"pid":"6fdf3cf6014efa37a2aa317748bb2b8695ef1aff","tid":2365411,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265c8714cf9d54d0473ff0e2da292533cfd059fd","tid":2365411,"uid":154486,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"吹咩你又告唔到佢<br />\nSection 230<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1b44681a0bde68d49dc4e1781cc24dc40b956c","tid":2365411,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d44f68991344e3c053236b74081ca63cc2979fc","tid":2365411,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"具有社會主義特色的澄清"},{"pid":"aa516f5354170f4cb41410311978a9da24fb8f24","tid":2365411,"uid":119218,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"Hi PR. 咁夜仲返工？"},{"pid":"6247aea7501b86ad4bb6881a9c00b0acae88e5eb","tid":2365411,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\